CREATE VIEW [business_rules].[xmlrelease_s_xmlinterface]
AS

  SELECT 
    bo.[business key for hub xmlrelease],                                        -- Business Key for Hub XMLRelease
    bo.[ps xmlrelease - xmlinterface - default of vi_xml_release_u_staging],     -- Entry Present in Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[lts xmlrelease - xmlinterface - default of vi_xml_release_u_staging],    -- Load Time Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[updated],                                                                -- [updated] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[product_name],                                                           -- [product_name] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[release_creationdatealm],                                                -- [release_creationdatealm] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[release_creationdatesvn],                                                -- [release_creationdatesvn] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[release_guid],                                                           -- [release_guid] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[release_lastmoddate],                                                    -- [release_lastmoddate] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[release_modtimealm],                                                     -- [release_modtimealm] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[release_revisionalm],                                                    -- [release_revisionalm] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[release_revisionsvn],                                                    -- [release_revisionsvn] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[release_version],                                                        -- [release_version] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[component_guid],                                                         -- [component_guid] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[component_cmppkgname],                                                   -- [component_cmppkgname] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING
    bo.[component_version]                                                       -- [component_version] from Satellite XMLRelease > XMLINTERFACE > Default of VI_XML_RELEASE_U_STAGING

  FROM [businessobjects].[xmlrelease_s_xmlinterface] AS bo
;
